    {
      "chinese": "至於女孩，她們在家學習各種技藝。從小就在家裡學習打掃庭院、洗衣、挑水、煮飯等事務；稍長成少女時，母親就開始教導她們編織、搗米、做栥粑、到海邊撿海瓜子、種菜、以及在家裡整理家務。我們阿美族是這樣教育我們的孩子。",
      "ab": "O fafahiyan sato a wawa i, i loma’ ko pihatatanaman nangra to kalodemak ato tayal. Nani kaemangan a mipacafay to tayal i loma’, miasik, mifaca’, miradom, mitangtang; masakaying to cangra i, pasifana’en to no wina a mitenooy, mitifek, misatoron, micekiw, misadateng, ato milosimet to maamaan a lalosidan i loma’. O hatiniay ko pipalatamdaw no malitengay no mita o ’Amis to kaemangay.",
